   6:reduce.c      **** * Name:        montgomery_reduce
   7:reduce.c      **** *
   8:reduce.c      **** * Description: Montgomery reduction; given a 32-bit integer a, computes
   9:reduce.c      **** *              16-bit integer congruent to a * R^-1 mod q,
  10:reduce.c      **** *              where R=2^16
  11:reduce.c      **** *
  12:reduce.c      **** * Arguments:   - int32_t a: input integer to be reduced;
  13:reduce.c      **** *                           has to be in {-q2^15,...,q2^15-1}
  14:reduce.c      **** *
  15:reduce.c      **** * Returns:     integer in {-q+1,...,q-1} congruent to a * R^-1 modulo q.
  16:reduce.c      **** **************************************************/
